{"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setUserId:completion:","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setUserId:completion:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:completion:"}],"title":"setUserId:completion:","role":"symbol"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","text":"NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"userId","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"completion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"text":" (^","kind":"text"},{"text":")(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError","text":"NSError"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"error"},{"kind":"text","text":")) "},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The custom user identifier (e.g., database ID, UUID, username).","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"userId"},{"name":"completion","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Block called when the operation completes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Same as "},{"code":"setUserId:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" but provides callback when the server operation completes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Use this when you need to ensure the user ID is set before performing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"dependent operations like merging user data or tracking critical events.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Example","text":"Example","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Handle login with guaranteed user ID synchronization:"}]},{"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing","code":["class LoginCoordinator {","","    func performLogin(credentials: Credentials,","                      completion: @escaping (Result<User, Error>) -> Void) {","","        APIClient.shared.login(credentials) { result in","            switch result {","            case .success(let user):","                \/\/ Set user ID with confirmation before proceeding","                Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(user.id) { error in","                    if let error = error {","                        Logger.warning(\"User ID sync failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                        \/\/ Continue anyway - local state is still valid","                    }","","                    \/\/ Now safe to track login event with correct user attribution","                    Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                        \"logged_in\": true,","                        \"last_login\": ISO8601DateFormatter().string(from: Date()),","                        \"login_method\": credentials.method.rawValue","                    ])","","                    \/\/ Set email if available","                    if let email = user.email {","                        Pushwoosh.configure.setEmail(email)","                    }","","                    completion(.success(user))","                }","","            case .failure(let error):","                completion(.failure(error))","            }","        }","    }","}"]}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets a custom user identifier with completion confirmation."}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"kind":"symbol","variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:completion:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:completion:"},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setUserId:completion:":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuserid:completion:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUserId:completion:"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUserId:completion:","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Sets a custom user identifier with completion confirmation.","type":"text"}],"title":"setUserId:completion:","type":"topic","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setUserId:completion:","kind":"identifier"}]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"type":"topic","title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","role":"collection"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"PWConfiguration","kind":"iden